Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是假定首都圈内发生强烈地震，\N以大量的研究和验证为基础制作的虚构故事。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了追求真实性，我们在构造原创故事时已做\N过很多模拟，但在演出上仍会有与真实情况不符之处。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些讨厌事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种世界干脆都给我崩坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我要上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 能站起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢点 慢点  看着脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受够了 什么都这么麻烦\N这种世界干脆都给我崩坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这傻站着！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 有没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有看到一个男孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定…还在厕所里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 悠贵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口就在前面 大家别慌慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 快回来 那边很危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的女孩子 快回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 不能去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的地震那边起火了 去西边避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险 真是千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚刚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人？ 刚刚和你在一起的弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所…我让他一个人去厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸妈妈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我和弟弟两个人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他一个人去厕所了 厕所里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是没人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君！ 悠贵君！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起找你弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为地震很强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 有看到一个男孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七八岁左右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子倒有看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都和父母在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 有看到一个男孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么高 七八岁左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着黄绿色 胸前有条线的T恤的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在1层的玩具屋看到几个一个人的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走别的楼梯吧 这里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这位姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 别那么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道那很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 悠贵在玩具屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道 但连你也受伤不就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「连你」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道悠贵就一定受伤了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那边危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 是我说错话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟没事 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一起找 所以别乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 大家没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没事 这太危险了你们也快去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我们在找一个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着黄绿色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们基本都找过了 这孩子是最后一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的估计已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回我话啊 悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我们先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险 趁还没被烟尘完全包围…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 要出去你就一个出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能放下悠贵不管！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想想 要怎么才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君要是活着肯定去避难了 所以你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要活着找到悠贵君不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 顺便买饮料回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 饮料！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这让我在这找找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 我在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 受伤没？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 马上救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抬住那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等雨停吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里太危险了 我们换个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生火灾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这就能避雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（拨号中…自家）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（请等待…）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不通？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是基站被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次为大家报道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距现在4小时前的15点46分左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以关东地区为中心发生了强烈地震
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次地震的震源是在东京湾北部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震源深度约25千米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示地震规模的震级据推测达到里氏8.0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里氏8.0？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请密切注意余震和海啸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受地震影响所有交通机构暂缓运行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外根据东京消防厅的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在都内各地发生大规模火灾 呼吁大家进行避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有避难时绝对不要使用汽车…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砧公园附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成城那边 我是在三轩茶屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 完全打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能收到的好像只有地面电视信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起想想怎么送你们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要对我们这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 因为人性？随便说说而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐啊 拼命在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点回家 把礼物送给妈妈才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 还没相互介绍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫日下部真理 你是悠贵君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小野沢未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来啊 真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不怎么喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢姐姐的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是国中生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你们两个一起出门 关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是 会变成这样全都是因为她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈老说工作工作的 叫我们两个自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话真刺耳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家是我妈妈和女儿三个人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也老是说工作工作 很少有时间陪女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿很喜欢秋千 我就想努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后搬到能放得下秋千的房子去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就在我这么磨磨蹭蹭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿或许就已经过了坐秋千的年龄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我去拿下东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把摩托车停在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人说不定就不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大姐姐没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也没义务照顾我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 这是余震了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大地震之后 余震会持续很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这次规模很小 这里没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说二位 肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 味道应该不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（生日快乐 雏）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天是我女儿的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就四岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状是彻底散了就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还是圆蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日蛋糕还是要买这种圆的才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 总之现在就先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也一定会很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨海大桥崩落 死伤多数
